    </div>
    <p class="stx-meta">Sources: US Census, Gallup, Harris Poll, World Bank, Numbeo · LeavingAmerica.co analysis · Updated {updated} · <a href="/methodology/">Methodology</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="stx-body">

