        <div class="stx-card stx-reveal"><div class="stx-num">5–9M</div><p>Americans are estimated to live outside the United States. No agency keeps an exact count, which is why estimates vary this widely.</p><span class="stx-src">Source: State Department & AARO estimates</span></div>
        <div class="stx-card stx-reveal"><div class="stx-num amber" data-count="1514" data-prefix="+" data-suffix="%">0</div><p>Spike in Google searches related to moving abroad in the days after the November 2024 US election.</p><span class="stx-src">Source: VisaGuide.World</span></div>
        <div class="stx-card stx-reveal"><div class="stx-num green" data-count="80" data-prefix="+" data-suffix="%">0</div><p>Year-over-year growth in new registrations reported by expat tax provider MyExpatTaxes for the 2026 season.</p><span class="stx-src">Source: <a href="https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/06/24/3317095/0/en/New-MyExpatTaxes-Data-Confirms-Trend-of-More-Americans-Moving-Abroad-Amid-Trump-Wave-Relocations.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MyExpatTaxes, 2026</a></span></div>
