        <div class="stx-faq-item"><button class="stx-faq-q" type="button" aria-expanded="false"><span>How many Americans live abroad?</span><span class="stx-faq-ic">+</span></button><div class="stx-faq-a" hidden><p>Estimates range from 5 to 9 million US citizens living outside the United States. No agency keeps an exact count. A 2026 US Census Bureau analysis estimated around 180,000 Americans moved abroad in the past year alone.</p></div></div>
